{"tid":657922,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"爆笑家族:令計劃 令方針 令政策 令路線","createTime":"2018-05-08T13:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T14:25:54.000Z","uid":36097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"58df6dd05337b5087ac2b67e906ea79078b30dad","tid":657922,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"3高官涉貪遭起訴 魏民洲傳與令計劃家族有私交<br />\n據明報報道，令氏兄弟是山西平陸人，其家族原姓令狐，似為少數民族後裔，後為方便去&ldquo;狐&rdquo;字簡化成姓&ldquo;令&rdquo;。令計劃父母均為當地基層幹部，父親原為山西省一名處級幹部，育有4子1女，名字分別是令路線、令政策、令方針、令計劃、令完成，其中令方針為女兒，令計劃為三子，令政策是次子。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n令方針 <br />\n令政策 <br />\n令路線 (女) <br />\n令計劃 <br />\n令完成 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2067585/3%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E6%B6%89%E8%B2%AA%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%20%E9%AD%8F%E6%B0%91%E6%B4%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%88%87%E4%BB%A4%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2067585%2F3%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B2%25AA%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%2520%25E9%25AD%258F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25A4&d=GtAXJ63CH5ngc%2FoJJJ3mSozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=613ab1e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2067585/3%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E6%B6%89%E8%B2%AA%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%20%E9%AD%8F%E6%B0%91%E6%B4%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%88%87%E4%BB%A4%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%A4</a>"},{"pid":"d06a52acedf9e9942edf5feb04a7e92c3a998025","tid":657922,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:37:31.000Z","msg":"令狐係少數民族？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪搞笑啦"},{"pid":"a4952ff894b2695e83377829b3072f37dac32096","tid":657922,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTim